msgid "For example, to deploy the native Java 17 version to OpenShift, simply run `+kubectl apply -f deploy/k8s/native-java17-openshift.yml+` (or `+oc apply -f deploy/k8s/native-java17-openshift.yml+`)."
msgstr "Por exemplo, para implantar a versão nativa do Java 17 no OpenShift, basta executar `kubectl apply -f deploy/k8s/native-java17-openshift.yml` (ou `oc apply -f deploy/k8s/native-java17-openshift.yml`)."

